title.narrative: Grazing Lands, Livestock and Climate Resilient Mitigation in the Kafue Basin

description.narrative: The Livestock project introduced the principle of holistic sustainable land management in Zambia, Zimbabwe, Mozambique and Malawi. In 2021, the project expanded to two new sites in Zambia as a result of the high demand by the communities after noticing the positive results, reaching a total of 435 farmers supported.
